{"type": "article", "id": 16565, "title": "坐凳", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-26T06:51:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000346JIgaxMyn0KTkGULX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是黎巴嫩设计师 Iyad Naja 带来的坐凳系列，正在迪拜设计周上展出。他用金属材质将阿拉伯字体做成镂空的图案，嵌在混凝土的坐凳中，有一种丰富的层次感，也是传统与现代的结合。阿拉伯文字的图案组成富有中东气息的装饰，华丽而有艺术感，并凸显出了材质的特征。这组凳子有金色、黑色和玫瑰色三种颜色。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143802niV8u9XotS02evOH.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"654\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614380257TVRAwXoQyhqmCG.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"654\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143803Hksgh2XGifpRnP6e.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"654\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261438034eGtZpcEuWBgolia.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"654\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261438045upmvRkHLNbrXcex.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1084\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.32518337\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}